org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.api.template

Interface TemplateMethod

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.annotation.Annotation

    The method level annotation used to mark a single method in an mediation template annotated with the MediationTemplate annotation at the class level.

    Note that there can only be one and only one method in a given template class with this annotation. Further the method annotated with this annotation can only have one of 3 following types of arguments;

    • Mediation
    • Message
    • Any parameter annotated with MessageProperty

    The optional result property specifies the string message property key to which the result of the template method invocation will be stored for further reference if the template method is not of void return type.

    Since:
    2.0.0
